ISLAMABAD, Nov 17 (APP): Minister for Information Chaudhry Fawad Hussain said on Wednesday that speeches of PML-N President Shahbaz Sharif and PPP Chairman Bilawal Bhutto Zardari were reflection of their defeat in today’s legislation process in the Parliament.
In a tweet he said after their speeches it has become clear now that who had majority in the Parliament and who were escaping.
